OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay "elated" after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,Fcampaigner Beckie Ramsay says she is
OL,7,F"elated" after the introduction of
OL,8,Fwater safety on the national
OL,9,Fcurriculum and said the lessons should
OL,10,F"help prevent future tragedies".
OL,12,FHer son Dylan, 13, a fit and strong
OL,13,Fswimmer, died within three minutes of
OL,14,Fentering water at Hilltop Quarry in
OL,15,FWhittle-le-Woods, close to his home in
OL,16,F.
OL,18,FHe had gone to cool down, but drowned
OL,19,Fafter suffering cold water shock.
