OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay "elated" after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,FEver since his death, 13-years-ago,
OL,7,FBeckie has campaigned for lessons in
OL,8,Fschools, which would include water
OL,9,Fsafety skills in the pool, as well as
OL,10,Flearning about cold water shock and
OL,11,Frip tides.
OL,13,FFollowing her son's death, Ms Ramsay,
OL,14,Fwho is from Lancashire, became a water
OL,15,Fsafety advocate and visits schools to
OL,16,Feducate children.
OL,18,FWater safety was officially added to
OL,19,Fthe national school curriculum last
OL,20,Fweek after she campaigned for the
OL,21,Fchange for 13 years.
