OL,3,CBeckie Ramsay "elated" after child
OL,4,Cwater campaign safety success
OL,6,F"I'm going nowhere, I'm going to
OL,7,Fcontinue doing what I'm doing but also
OL,8,Fbroaden my horizons. Look at water
OL,9,Fsafety equipment and continue to lobby
OL,10,Fparliament. This is just the start."
OL,12,FOn average, 400 people drown in the UK
OL,13,Feach year and another 200 people take
OL,14,Ftheir own lives in water, according to
OL,15,Fthe National Water Safety Forum.
